<p>Our Mexico office recently came together for a cause that hits close to home. A nearby animal shelter was struggling to keep up with daily demands, and the team didn't hesitate to step in.</p>
<p>Some employees spent the day on-site, feeding and caring for the animals, making sure every dog and cat got the attention they deserved. Others contributed financially to help the shelter cover essentials like food, medical supplies, and cleaning materials. Every bit made a real difference.</p>
<p>Acts like this aren't about recognition. They're about showing up for the community that supports us. We know how fortunate we are, and giving back is one way we stay grounded and connected. The Mexico team proved once again that compassion is part of who we are as a company.</p>
